==Mission highlights==
{| style=&quot;float: right&quot;
|-
|[[Image:Bean Descends Intrepid - GPN-2000-001317.jpg|thumb|235px|Alan Bean descends from the LM]]
|-
|[[Image:Apollo12Visor.jpg|thumb|235px|Alan Bean pictured by Pete Conrad (reflected in Bean's helmet)]]
|-
