== Depiction in popular culture ==
Portions of the Apollo 15 mission are dramatized in the miniseries ''[[From the Earth to the Moon (miniseries)|From the Earth to the Moon]]'' episode entitled [[From the Earth to the Moon (miniseries)#Episodes|&quot;Galileo was Right&quot;]].

